  m_Name: FomoSO 3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::FomoFirewallSO
  Question: Meme stock trending online.
  Desc: A famous influencer posted about the stock.No company news has been released.
  cmt1: Going to the moon!
  cmt2: Diamond hands!
  cmt3: Everyone is buying!
  CorrectOption: 3
  CorrectWhatHappenDec: The stock crashed after the online hype faded. Ignoring the
    emotional crowd protected your money.
  CorrectLesson: Social media trends are not reliable investment signals.
  WrongWhatHappenDec: You followed the online hype without any fundamental reason.
    The excitement quickly disappeared and the price fell sharply.
  WrongLesson: Don't invest based only on internet popularity.
